##16.1
1.
```{r}
New<-
  BabyNames%>%
  filter(sex!="F")%>%
  group_by(name)%>%
  summarise(total=sum(count))%>%
  extractMatches("([aeiou])$",name)%>%
  arrange(desc(total))
New%>%
head(10)
```

New1%>%
  head()
